---
title: Debian for WSL
---

```bash
# 开发必装
sudo apt install -y git curl wget python3 man neovim

# 转换 Windows 格式的换行符
sudo apt install -y dos2unix

# 命令缺失提示
sudo apt install -y command-not-found
sudo apt update
exec $SHELL

# 其他推荐
sudo apt install -y tree unzip tig
```

